2
00:00:02,700 --> 00:00:05,500
We have come a long way in
our improvement journey.

3
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:08,530
For us, it may have been
10 or 20 minutes of video,

4
00:00:08,530 --> 00:00:10,630
but in real life, we may
have just spent three

5
00:00:10,630 --> 00:00:13,000
to six months to create and
implement the improvement

6
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,320
we wanted to see.

7
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:16,440
Now it's time to check in on our progress

8
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:19,080
and see if we made a positive
or a negative change.

9
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:21,670
The sixth step, did we get there,

10
00:00:21,670 --> 00:00:23,690
involves checking our new normal.

11
00:00:23,690 --> 00:00:25,450
Basically, where are we today,

12
00:00:25,450 --> 00:00:27,460
